# CIP-0023 — Fair Min Fees

> **CIP-0023 · Fair Min Fees** · 2021 · Shawn McMurdo, Ryan Wiley · adds one parameter `minPoolMargin` · no hard fork · **No-go as a standalone — the same mechanism is already inside CIP-0082 stage 2**
