| CIP-0023.S2.F1 | [D] | **Standalone variant compresses productive-range delegator fee-rate dispersion 38× → 13×.** Partial delivery on the §3.3 delegator-yield claim | [B.1](#b1-s2-partial-cps-coverage-and-regressive-transfer-up-the-distribution) |
| **CIP-0023.S3** | | **Blind spot at the below-floor tail — the instrument does not reach the struggling population it is meant to help** | [B.2](#b2-s3-below-floor-tail-untouched) |
